org.eclipse.rdf4j.sparqlbuilder.rdf

Class Rdf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.rdf4j.sparqlbuilder.rdf.Rdf

  • public class Rdf
extends Object
    A class with static methods to create basic SparqlBuilder RDF objects from either string values or RDF4J Model objects.
